milestones.description: Viv Richards has scored 5 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for WI breaking Clive Lloyd's record
Viv Richards's 153 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for WI), surpassing Haynes's 148
Deryck Murray has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (19) for WI, going past Clive Lloyd
Viv Richards and Haynes's 205-run partnership is the highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 176 between Dennis Amiss and Fletcher
Viv Richards and Haynes's 205-run partnership is WI's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 149 between Clive Lloyd and Rohan Kanhai
Viv Richards and Haynes's 205-run partnership is WI's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 143 between Fredericks and Alvin Kallicharran
Viv Richards and Haynes's 205-run partnership is the highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 182 between Alan Turner and Rick McCosker
